org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class tensorflow.ResourceStridedSliceAssign

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.tensorflow.ResourceStridedSliceAssign
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    tensorflow

    @Namespace(value="tensorflow::ops")
 @NoOffset
public static class tensorflow.ResourceStridedSliceAssign
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    Assign value to the sliced l-value reference of ref. The values of value are assigned to the positions in the variable ref that are selected by the slice parameters. The slice parameters begin, end, strides, etc. work exactly as in StridedSlice. NOTE this op currently does not support broadcasting and so value's shape must be exactly the shape produced by the slice of ref. Arguments: * scope: A Scope object Returns: * the created Operation{@code
